&lt;p&gt;The Marketing Team is taking care of customer acquisition and customer retention for Raisin’s international savings and investments platforms. It is focussing on understanding the journey of (potential) customers and on communicating the value of Raisin&#39;s services across different marketing channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Director Brand Marketing is responsible for building out the Brand Marketing discipline at Raisin. It is a great opportunity for somebody who is eager to shape the perception of Raisin’s B2C platforms in multiple countries. This is a new role and while we already started to invest significantly into brand building there is a lot more we want to achieve in this area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is fundamental to help scaling our business in an effective and efficient manner, driving engagement of prospects and existing customers. It will be reporting directly to the CMO.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and evolve the global brand marketing strategy to build out a consistent positioning of the Raisin brand and to help fulfill ambitious growth targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the creative process of developing strong campaign ideas, driving customer acquisition and customer engagement. Lead campaigns, from creative development to execution and measurement across geographies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead media planning and buying, building a systematic approach to define the right media mix while using negotiation tactics to deliver best possible ROI on media investments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring our brand framework to life across all channels—paid, owned and earned, aligning with our design team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive insights-based decision-making by partnering with Performance Marketing, Design, Product, Content and Communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and mentor a high-performing team, fostering creativity, collaboration, and professional growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee agency partnerships (creative and media) and ensure high-quality deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor brand performance KPIs and translate insights into actionable improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the brand internally, inspiring teams across the company to live our brand values.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in brand marketing, brand strategy, or integrated marketing, ideally in a fast-growing consumer-facing environment with international scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success in developing large-scale brand campaigns and in systematically evolving a brand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership experience with proven ability to develop and inspire creative and strategic teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep analyt

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;sc-gEkIjz cjtSrT MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 sc-hoLEA&quot;&gt;Raisin is the world’s leading platform for savings and investment products. Founded in 2012, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;FinTech&lt;/strong&gt; connects consumers with banks in the EU, the UK and the US. This gives consumers &lt;strong&gt;better interest rates&lt;/strong&gt; and banks a &lt;strong&gt;diversified form of refinancing&lt;/strong&gt;. Our vision is to offer savings and investments without barriers and thus open up the global 160 trillion euro market.&lt;/p&gt;
