&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You bring at least 1 year of leadership or people management experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You successfully managed software projects, build sustainable software and delivered in collaborative fashion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You feel comfortable and confident driving technical and architectural discussions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a decisive leader who stands your ground on architectural integrity while remaining a pragmatic and collaborative problem-solver.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You foster a culture of ownership, accountability, and technical excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
