&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Academic Background: University degree in Law, Economics, Business Administration, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional Experience: Extensive experience in Anti-Financial Crime (AFC) within the financial services industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regulatory Expertise: In-depth knowledge of national and international regulatory frameworks (e.g., German GwG, KWG, and EU AML Directives).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process Excellence: Proven experience in designing, documenting, and optimising AFC processes and frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Language

