&lt;li&gt;You have shared responsibility for finding the best ways to give our customers exposure to new asset classes, including instrument screening and selection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll analyse data using quantitative and qualitative methods to learn more about our customers and their investment behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You serve as a point of contact for all things capital markets for all Raisin stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You represent the team’s investment philosophy throughout the organization and externally.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
